# Components

## Layering (prefer this order)

1. **`components/ui/`** — shadcn/Radix primitives (`Button`, `Sheet`, `Dialog`, `Table`). Do not duplicate.
2. **`components/`** — cross-domain shared UI.
3. **`features/{domain}/`** — domain screens, rows, dialogs.
4. **`pages/`** — thin Inertia entry only (see `pages.mdc`).

## Prefer

| Need | Use | Reference |
|------|-----|-----------|
| List header | `PageHeader` | `components/page-header.tsx` |
| Search | `SearchBar` | `components/search-bar.tsx` |
| Show page header | `DetailsHeader` | `components/details-header.tsx` |
| Empty lists | `EmptyState` | `components/empty-state.tsx` |
| Pagination | `Pagination` | `components/pagination.tsx` |
| Export | `ExportMenu` | `components/export-menu.tsx` |
| Grid/table toggle | `ViewToggle` | `components/view-toggle.tsx` |
| Field errors | `InputError` | `components/input-error.tsx` |
| Selects | `AppSelect` | `components/app-select.tsx` |
| Audit section | `RecentActivityCard` | `components/recent-activity-card.tsx` |
| Class merging | `cn()` | `lib/utils.ts` |
| Design tokens | `lib/design-system.ts`, `glass-card` | `resources/css/design-system.css` |

## Naming

- PascalCase exports: `BranchFormSheet`, `DocumentComplianceTableRow`.
- Suffix by role: `*-form-sheet`, `*-delete-dialog`, `*-filters-sheet`, `*-table-row`, `*-content`.

## File placement

```
features/organization/branches/
  index.tsx              ← screen body
  types.ts
  components/
    branch-form-sheet.tsx
    branch-delete-dialog.tsx
```

- **Cross-domain** → `resources/js/components/`.
- **Domain-only** → `features/{domain}/components/` or `features/{domain}/shared/`.

## Avoid

- New UI libraries alongside shadcn/Radix.
- TanStack Table — use `OrganizationDataTable` (see `tables.mdc`).
- Inline duplicate of `ConfirmDeleteDialog`, `FiltersSheet`, or `ListTableCrudActions`.
- Narration comments; match sibling file style.

## Golden references

- List screen: `features/organization/branches/index.tsx`
- Form sheet styling: `features/organization/branches/components/branch-form-sheet.tsx`
- Detail page: `pages/organization/branch.tsx`
- Document row actions: `features/organization/documents/shared/document-actions/document-list-row-actions.tsx`
